prompt: Read the file config.yaml and extract all key-value pairs.
teacher_text:
I don't have direct access to your file system, so I cannot read the `config.yaml` file directly. Could you please provide the content of the file? You can paste it here, and I will extract all key-value pairs for you.

For example, if your `config.yaml` looks like this:

```yaml
database:
  host: localhost
  port: 5432
  username: admin
  password: secret123
app:
  name: MyApp
  debug: true
  timeout: 30
```

I would extract:

```
database.host: localhost
database.port: 5432
database.username: admin
database.password: secret123
app.name: MyApp
app.debug: true
app.timeout: 30
```

Please paste the content of your `config.yaml` file, and I'll parse it for you.
